snippet.title: The Lightning Seeds - Three Lions '98 (Official Video)
snippet.description:
Lightning Seeds - Three Lions '98 (Official Video) Listen on Spotify http://smarturl.it/TLFS_Spot

Follow The Lightning Seeds
Website - http://www.thelightningseeds.net/
Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/thelightningseeds/
Twitter - https://twitter.com/Lightning_Seeds
Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/lightningseedsofficial/

Lyrics
We still believe, we still believe
We still believe, we still believe
It's coming home, it's coming home
It's coming, Football's coming home
It's coming home, it's coming home
It's coming, Football's coming home again
Tears for heroes dressed in grey
No plans for final day
Stay in bed, drift away
It could have been all
Songs in the street
It was nearly complete
It was nearly so sweet
And now I'm singing
Three lions on a shirt
Jules remains still gleaming
No more years of hurt
No more need for dreaming
Talk about football coming home
And then one night in Rome
We were strong, we had grown
And now I see Ince ready for war
Gazza good as before
Shearer certain to score
And Psycho screaming
Three lions on a shirt
Jules remains still gleaming
No more years of hurt
No more need for dreaming
We can dance Nobby's dance
We could dance it in France
It's coming home, it's coming home
It's coming, Football's coming home
